'''At Weɣlis''' (FR : Ait Weghlis ) d lɛerc i d-yekkan tama n wedrar n [[Akfadu (adrar)| wekfadu]] 

==Azar n wawal==

Amezruy n lɛerc n '''at Weɣlis''' ibedd ɣef kard(3) n tmucuha, llant snat sɛant yiwen n uẓeɣzen ameẓli deg umezruy (raisonnement logique en histoire), yiwet teqqen ɣer [[Ulysse]], tayeḍ teqqen ɣer '''wekyis''', qqaren-d belli s ya i d-yussa n wawal n '''weɣlis'''.
Timucuha-agi nesebrurz it-ent deg ḥric n umezruy.

